data.title: Fox Girls Presents | We Live - Way of the Road Fall 2013
data.description:
All restraints removed, living a wild ride, sharing a common bond. It's the way of the road. Free spirits, adventurous attitudes and the freedom of exploring the land. With four wheels moving our body and two wheels moving our soul. WE LIVE.

Shot on Location in Los Angeles, California

Models: 
Abby Brothers 
Lauren Young

Featuring Fox Athletes: 
Adam Jones, FMX
Chase Hawk, BMX
Drew Bezanson, BMX
Jimmy LaRiche, Wake
Sean Sexton, BMX
Zachary "Catfish" Yankush, BMX

Music:
The Mynabirds
"Generals" 
Generals

data.title: Fox Footwear Presents | The Featherlite
data.description:
The Featherlite combines the lightweight attributes of a racing flat with the cushion, flexibility, and support of a high-performance distance runner. The result is a truly authentic performance running shoe that can meet the serious training needs of our world-class action sports athletes.

• 3D asymmetrical structure to serve the natural movement of the foot.
• Super Breathable Mesh Upper for maximum breathability.
• Ultra light full-length Skylyte midsole for superior cushioning.
• Visible Heel Strike Foam provides shock absorption while enhancing stability during the strike phase.
• Mid-foot Flex Tendon provides arch support, increases stability, and conserves energy during the transfer phase.
• Forefoot Rebound Foam maximizes energy return during the launch phase to aid propulsion and enhance endurance.
• Duratrak MDT outsole for excellent grip and durability.

data.title: Fox Footwear Presents | The Motion Varial
data.description:
The Motion Varial fuses athletic footwear technology, construction, and comfort with the best in casual footwear styling. This is lifestyle reimagined.

• Modern athletic construction and MX heritage elevate this casual style.
• Mesh instep provides breathability, and the unique cage structure provides support while reducing weight.
• Fox Motion technology provides superior cushion, comfort, and flexibility, while drastically reducing weight.
• Decoupled outsole features nine Motion flex grooves for a level of flexibility that is unmatched in the category.
• Duratrak MDT outsole for excellent grip and durability.

Music: 
Artist: Pretty Lights 
Song: Still Night 
Album Title: Glowing In The Darkest Night 
Red Light Management
